#inline#mFMb_DS_Toggle( boolean )/*	What it does:	It toggles the DoScript plug-in on or off		Required parameters:	boolean, True or False		returns:		nothing if the syntax is correct			evaluation error 14 (out of range) if the boolean is not 0 or 1		notes:		Try to construct a validation formula for a trigger that 			- disables DoScript			- EvaluationError ( Evaluate () ) the formula			- enables DoScript			in one go, using a Let() construction*/